# LoTN V5 SRD reference

When changing Laws of the Night V5 rules, data, or generation logic:

## Authority order

1. **OWOD SRD** — https://www.oneworldofdarkness.com/laws-of-the-night/  
   In Cursor chat: `@LoTN V5 SRD` (after adding the URL under Settings → Features → Docs)
2. **`reference/lotn_v5/SRD_INDEX.md`** — deep links to SRD sections
3. **`reference/lotn_v5/RULES_INDEX.md`** — maps PDF sections to JSON under `wod_chargen/games/lotn_v5/data/`
4. **Local pocket PDF** (`reference/lotn_v5/*.pdf`, gitignored) — optional offline detail

## Key SRD entry points for this project

| Topic | SRD |
|-------|-----|
| Character creation & XP | `/dramatic-systems/character-creation` |
| Ghouls | `/dramatic-systems/ghouls` |
| Clans | `/clans` |
| Disciplines | `/disciplines` |
| Backgrounds | `/backgrounds` |
| Predator types | `/predator-types` |
| Thin-blood | `/thin-blood` |
| Merits/flaws | `/merits-flaws` |

Full URL list: `reference/lotn_v5/SRD_INDEX.md`

## Implementation notes

- Canonical game data lives in `wod_chargen/games/lotn_v5/data/*.json` — not inline in `app/`.
- After adding packaged JSON/Python, run `python scripts/generate_pyscript_config.py`.
- Validate archetypes: `python scripts/validate_archetypes.py`
- Do not commit copyrighted PDFs; SRD URLs are the public reference.
